{"tid":2131030,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊明食店生意額跌4成 不排除關分店","createTime":"2020-07-29T14:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T01:39:32.000Z","uid":128369,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd848debf33efd9b0e0a0b90409d851f160a3ac","tid":2131030,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"今天（29日）是政府實施除特定處所外，其他食店全日禁堂食首日，身為食店老闆的楊明出席劇集宣傳活動時表示，現時有很多食店事情處理，未看到實質數字，不過之前限制晚市堂食期間，5間舖的生意額共下跌3、4成：「雖然不是很樂觀，但希望配合政府措施抗疫，齊心協力捱過去。（最壞打算會否先關掉一、兩間？）不排除，但暫時都希望長工有工開，亦會縮短營業時間，讓員工在這段時間多留在家。<br />\n<br />\n一定無事會開勻全港18區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSource:[url]<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200729/1596027524266/%E3%80%90%E5%85%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F%E3%80%91%E6%A5%8A%E6%98%8E%E9%A3%9F%E5%BA%97%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E9%A1%8D%E8%B7%8C4%E6%88%90-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E9%97%9C%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200729%2F1596027524266%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%25A1%258D%25E8%25B7%258C4%25E6%2588%2590-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6165b44d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200729%2F1596027524266%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%25A1%258D%25E8%25B7%258C4%25E6%2588%2590-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597&h=747